parameters:
Mage Relm: We got on the ship... but I can hardly see the
other ship. Is it okay!?
Thief Nora: W-We might get away~!

Cors the Wanderer: Well, well, calm down. This here is a
specialized ship for transporting dangerous goods, you know.

Cors the Wanderer: I have a little trick up my sleeve, you
know.

Mage Relm: A gigantic crystal... Could it be using magic
power...?!

Cors the Wanderer: Oh, these are clever folks. When you
unleash the magic power of this thing, fun things are likely
to happen.

Mage Relm: Everyone, please hold onto something! The ship
will experience a sudden acceleration with explosive magical
power!!

Mage Relm: W-Wait, this speed!? Ahh, I'm gonna die, I'm
being thrown off!!

Clea: The sea breeze feels so nice. I'm impressed that we
were able to get on the ship today.

Cors the Wanderer: Ahaha, we get along well, don't we? It's
a rare opportunity, so let's enjoy ourselves.

Priestess Sophia: Indeed, such a strong wind... hehe, it
feels like cutting through the blue sea--

Mage Relm: Whoa, hey, don't throw it over here! Please don't
send it flying towards me!!
Clea: Is this what they call a hangover?

Cors the Wanderer: No, no, this is what they call
seasickness, you know.

Cors the Wanderer: Oh, the ship is approaching, guys. Let's
tie up the ship as usual!

Mage Relm: Ahh, another unknown language!? Wait, stop it,
someone, please stop it!!
